tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ecosystem_data (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    species_name VARCHAR(255),
    ecosystem_type VARCHAR(255),
    habitat VARCHAR(255),
    latitude DECIMAL(10, 8),
    longitude DECIMAL(11, 8),
    temperature FLOAT,
    humidity FLOAT,
    precipitation FLOAT,
    biodiversity_index INTEGER
);

CREATE TABLE ecosystem_data (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    species_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    habitat VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    temperature FLOAT NOT NULL,
    humidity FLOAT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE biodiversity_predictions (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    species_id INT NOT NULL,
    prediction_date DATE NOT NULL,
    predicted_population INT NOT NULL,
    confidence_level FLOAT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Species_data (
  species_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  species_name VARCHAR(255),
  species_population INT,
  ecosystem_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (ecosystem_id) REFERENCES Ecosystem_data(ecosystem_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Machine_learning (
  ml_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ml_algorithm VARCHAR(255),
  accuracy_score FLOAT,
  species_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (species_id) REFERENCES Species_data(species_id)
);

CREATE TABLE biodiversity_data (
  ecosystem_id INT,
  species_id INT,
  abundance INT,
  CONSTRAINT fk_ecosystem FOREIGN KEY (ecosystem_id) REFERENCES ecosystems(id),
  CONSTRAINT fk_species FOREIGN KEY (species_id) REFERENCES species(id)
);

CREATE TABLE EcosystemData (
  ecosystem_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ecosystem_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  biodiversity_index FLOAT NOT NULL,
  species_count INT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE HabitatData (
  habitat_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ecosystem_id INT REFERENCES EcosystemData(ecosystem_id),
  habitat_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  temperature FLOAT NOT NULL,
  rainfall FLOAT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE SpeciesData (
  species_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  species_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  habitat_id INT REFERENCES HabitatData(habitat_id),
  population_size INT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE PredictionModel (
  model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  accuracy FLOAT NOT NULL,
  training_data_size INT NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE BiodiversityPatterns (
  pattern_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  ecosystem_id INT REFERENCES EcosystemData(ecosystem_id),
  model_id INT REFERENCES PredictionModel(model_id),
  biodiversity_score FLOAT NOT NULL
)
